{"tid":565788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳曼琪：學好普通話是民族、歷史責任","createTime":"2018-02-19T10:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T12:22:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"26edf460a1f2fe5b490e375da6a7315badb5e586","tid":565788,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180219/s00001/c4c8e257c6ea61a9cebc48efa19c19e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180219%2Fs00001%2Fc4c8e257c6ea61a9cebc48efa19c19e9.jpg&h=bc9bd802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學習普通話問題近日引起熱論。反佔中律師、當選港區人大代表的陳曼琪表示，學好普通話是民族、歷史及中國人責任。<br />\n<br />\n曼琪接受《港人講地》訪問指出，最近有一小撮青年抗拒學普通話，校園內亦有涉及「港獨」言行，認為應阻止這些事情蔓延，強調「認同身分」對青年人、每個人都重要，學好普通話則是民族、歷史、中國人責任。<br />\n<br />\n陳曼琪另稱，「守法依法」意思是「香港是國家一部分，言論自由集會自由，必須受制於國家安全及完整之下」，形容國家昌隆是作為中國人的光榮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180219/s00001/1519030188873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180219%2Fs00001%2F1519030188873&d=dPt5hoR%2F8%2FipJ5OUgle%2BkGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ecaa34ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180219%2Fs00001%2F1519030188873&h=66917fe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180219/s00001/1519030188873</a>"},{"pid":"b5e423a02080c64498713f59e8d803fb618fb2a2","tid":565788,"uid":49392,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"睇咗做陳曼娜"},{"pid":"a603ab900f99c93ce8f3c34997d386b9a1396c41","tid":565788,"uid":54733,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"民你老母族咩<br />\n<br />\n我祖先講廣東話架"},{"pid":"fccd50c8e0bf8fe21efa65321c0e1d186471b9f1","tid":565788,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re